<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>REVIVE THY WORK, O LORD!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Na nasep hihhalh in!
 Na mithieng te'n muu hen!
 Mitin lunggil ah thu genin,
 Na mite chun zau hen!

[V2]
 Na nasep hihhalh in,
 Na maah ka khun ui!
 Lungsietna Lalpa hungkum in,
 Hungin, vang ei hung pie'n!

[V3]
 2. Na nasep hihhalh in,
 Na minlun chawisang in!
 Mi lunggil ah Na hehpihna,
 Mei bangin hung kuong hen!

[V4]
 3. Na nasep hihhalh in,
 Na thu mi cheng, vangpie'n;
 A thienna, A dikna thuguk,
 Ginna hingin lang hen!

[V5]
 4. Na nasep hihhalh in,
 Penticost guoh zu hen!
 Lopina Nang maia hi hen,
 Vangpiekna keihaw di'n.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>216</hymn_number>
</song>